#

Loaded Baked Potatoes

70 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasyVegetarian

Description

Creamy, fluffy baked potatoes topped with cheese, sour cream, and chives for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • chives: 1/4 cup chopped
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
